-- A feature group type declaration does not declare any prototypes and features with the same
-- defining identifier. No bug SC0009.
PACKAGE FEATURE_GROUP_TYPE_DECLARATION_TC2
    PUBLIC
        FEATURE GROUP f_group_declaration
            PROTOTYPES
                feature_prototype : FEATURE;

                component_prototype : DATA;
            FEATURES
                feature_declaration : IN DATA PORT;
                in_feature : IN DATA PORT;
                out_feature : OUT DATA PORT;            
        END f_group_declaration;
END FEATURE_GROUP_TYPE_DECLARATION_TC2;
